      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 18</em>, <em>PRPG Core Rulebook pg. 142</em></p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"https://www.aonprd.com/images/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\">Statistics</h3><p><strong>Cost</strong> 10 gp <strong>Weight</strong> 6 lbs.</p><p><strong>Damage</strong> 1d6 (small), 1d8 (medium); <strong>Critical</strong> x3; <strong>Range</strong> -; <strong>Type</strong> S; <strong>Special</strong> -</p><p><strong>Category</strong> One-Handed; <strong>Proficiency</strong> Martial</p><p><strong>Weapon Groups</strong> Axes</p><h3 class=\"framing\">Description</h3><p>The handle of this axe is long enough that you can wield it one-handed or two-handed. The head may have one blade or two, with blade shapes ranging from half-moons to squared edges like narrower versions of woodcutting axes. The wooden haft may be protected and strengthened with metal bands called langets.</p>"
